    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>New Client Special | PixelBrew - Virtual Tech Assistance</title>
</head>
<body class="font-sans bg-gray-50 overflow-x-hidden">
    <Header />
    <div class="bg-base-100 flex items-center justify-center">
        <section class="container mx-auto px-8 lg:px-0 py-16">
            <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl w-full lg:w-1/3 text-primary font-neuebit leading-[2rem]">New Client Special</h1>
        </section>
        </div>
    <section class="bg-neutral" id="professional">
        <div class="container mx-auto lg:py-16 text-base-100">
            <p>Get 20% off your first three tasks!</p>
            <p>The first task will be billed immediately after it is marked as Completed, and subsequent tasks will be billed through autopay via Stripe on the first Monday of the month.</p>
            <p>Price Breakdown</p>
            <p>I charge $40/hour, billed in 15 minute increments. Each task will be billed for the tracked time. For example:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Task 1: 30 minutes - Regular Rate $20 / Discounted Rate $16</li>
                <li>Task 2: 1 hour - Regular Rate $40 / Discounted Rate $32</li>
                <li>Task 3: 15 minutes - Regular Rate $10 / Discounted Rate $8</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Or any combination of the above!</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <script src="//code.tidio.co/tdv8h5nvfvmunnpiatdnog3kzoprjp4w.js" async></script>
</body>
</html>